docs.abstract: Celso Heredia, elderly man found wandering by the Brooklyn-Queens Expressway in June without any identification, disappears from Long Island College Hospital in Brooklyn Heights under mysterious circumstances; Heredia, who has no memory of his identity or where he came from, was one of last remaining patients in the hospital, and disappeared amid jockeying over facility's impending shutdown.

headline.main: Amid Hospital’s Turmoil, a Lost Man Disappears
